room_title: Escape room "Zombie Garage" by Trapped! Escape Room in Cleveland
room_address: 3301 East Royalton Rd, Broadview Heights, OH 44147
room_description: The dead are walking among us, but the answer to human victory can be found at a backwoods mechanic's garage. Bob the mechanic just finished making the ultimate zombie killing device but was zombified before he could activate the weapon. This plague will devour the planet if you can't activate the Zombie Killing Machine in the next 60 minutes. Can you prevent the zombie apocalypse?
